      "body": "https://www.ietf.org/archive/id/draft-ietf-spice-sd-cwt-00.html#name-acknowledgments\r\n\r\nhas anyone else worked on similar items for providing selective disclosure mechanisms in JSON? \r\n\r\nasking for a friend :) one who believes he's done some work on https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-oauth-selective-disclosure-jwt/ ",
