      "mergedBy": null,
      "mergeCommit": null,
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "rohanmahy",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "body": "sent to spice mailing list:\r\n\"A made three small technical changes, for which I will create issues after I take a break.\r\n\r\n1) The text in this PR says that the Issuer has to send the Salted Disclosed Claims for every digest in an SD-CWT. If not the Issuer could issue claims that the Holder can never verify that could be embarrassing or false (like \"Alice still likes the boy band of her youth\", or \"Rohan thinks the earth is flat\").\r\n2) I questioned if a CWT with no blinded claims can be an SD-CWT. My conclusion was no, so I changed the cardinality to at least 1 blinded claim. Of course you can disclose between zero and all of them.\r\n3) I left a hook to allow us to trivially add Decoy Digests\r\n\r\nI can change any of these things. Changing 1 and 3 are pretty trivial, and Changing 2 is still straightforward.\"",
          "createdAt": "2024-09-06T11:38:30Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-09-06T11:38:30Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "selfissued",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "body": "The acronym \"EDN\" is used without being expanded.  And there's no citation to its definition.\r\n\r\nPlease expand the acronym on first use *and* provide a citation.",
          "createdAt": "2024-09-06T16:46:40Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-09-06T16:46:40Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "rohanmahy",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "body": "> The acronym \"EDN\" is used without being expanded. And there's no citation to its definition.\r\n> \r\n> Please expand the acronym on first use _and_ provide a citation.\r\n\r\nHi Mike,\r\nThere is an expansion of EDN in PR #8 which would come earlier in the document. I just added a reference there in [this commit](https://github.com/ietf-wg-spice/draft-ietf-spice-sd-cwt/pull/8/commits/f0b7e8ec750e5c21d34a2d59752f376751258aa8). I'll leave this comment open in case this PR is merged but #8 is not.",
          "createdAt": "2024-09-06T17:46:42Z",
